title: FortiSwitch: Memory Usage
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/fortinet
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors memory usage of Fortinet FortiSwitch devices via the
 FORTINET-FORTISWITCH-MIB (used/total, .1.3.6.1.4.1.12356.106.4.1.3.0
 and .4.0). The service reports usage in percent with absolute values
 and provides perfdata for long-term trending, which is the primary
 signal for detecting slow memory leaks on embedded platforms.

 Upper WARN/CRIT levels are configurable via the "FortiSwitch memory
 usage" ruleset (default 80%/90%).

discovery:
 One service is created if the device reports memory values.
